          "text": "Measure inner diameter of camshaft bearing. Standard inner diameter (intake and exhaust): No. 1 bearing: 28.000 - 28.021 mm (1.1024 - 1.1032 in). No. 2 to No. 5 bearings: 23.500 - 23.521 mm (0.9252 - 0.9260 in).",
